d <- d %>% mutate(住院时间 = as.numeric(出院时间 - 入院时间) + 1)

dates <- as.POSIXct(c("1981-05-31", "2020-02-22"))
# 元素遍历
for(date in dates){
  print(date)
}
## [1] 360086400
## [1] 1582300800
# 下标遍历
for (i in 1:length(dates)) {
    print(dates[i])
}
## [1] "1981-05-31 CST"
## [1] "2020-02-22 CST"

n <- 1
while (log(n) <= 2) {
    print(log(n))
    n <- n + 1
}

## [1] 0.6931472
## [1] 1.098612

## [1] 1.94591
n <- 1
repeat {
    log_value <- log(n)
    if (log_value > 2) {
        break
    }
    print(log_value)
    n <- n + 1
}

1.

psi <- function(x) {
  ifelse(abs(x) <= 1, x^2, 2 * abs(x) - 1)
}

par(mar = c(5, 5, 4, 2) + 0.1)
curve(psi, from = -5, to = 5, col = "blue", lwd = 2, 
      ylab = "ψ(x)", xlab = "x", main = "Graph of ψ(x)")
grid(nx = NULL, ny = NULL, col = "gray", lty = "dotted")

2.

# 定义函数
S_kn <- function(k, n) {
  sum(1 / (1:n)^k)
}
n <- 5000000
k_values <- 2:21

# 不使用并行
system.time({
  results_non_parallel <- sapply(k_values, S_kn, n = n)
})
##    user  system elapsed 
##   1.450   0.073   1.527
# 使用并行
library(parallel, warn.conflicts = FALSE)
no_cores <- detectCores()
cl <- makeCluster(no_cores)
system.time({
  clusterExport(cl, varlist = c("n", "S_kn"))
  results_parallel <- parSapply(cl, k_values, S_kn, n = n)
})
##    user  system elapsed 
##   0.002   0.001   0.538
stopCluster(cl)
